# =============================================================================
# PicoClaw — Environment Variables Template
# =============================================================================
# USAGE:
#   cp .env.template .env
#   Fill in your real values in .env
#   Never commit .env to git
#
# PicoClaw reads these automatically via the PICOCLAW_* env var system,
# OR you can load them before starting:
#   source .env && picoclaw gateway
#   -- or --
#   set -a; source .env; set +a; picoclaw gateway
# =============================================================================

